* [[2018 AH]], largest asteroid to pass so close to Earth since 1972 on 2018-06-02.
* A106fgF, unconfirmed potential impactor on 2018-01-22.
* 2018 RC, near earth asteroid on 2018-09-03 (notable because it was discovered more than a day prior to closest approach on 2018-09-09). <ref>{{MPC|2018+RC|Minor Planet Center records for 2018 RC}}</ref>

