{{short description|sacred plant in Hindu belief}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2018}}
{{Infobox deity<!--Wikipedia:WikiProject Hindu mythology-->
| type        = Hindu
| image       = Tulsidevi01.jpg
| name = Tulsi
| caption      = Personification of Tulsi.
| Sanskrit_transliteration = {{IAST|Tulasi}}
| affiliation = [[Devi]] and [[Avatar]] of [[Lakshmi]]
|symbol = [[Holy basil|The Tulsi plant]]
| god_of      = The Tulsi plant
| abode       = The Tulsi plant and [[Vaikuntha]]
